title: Lobster Cove, Manchester, Massachusetts
medium: Brush and oil paint on wood panel
description: A view of a rocky cove, with a pale-blue sky and pinkish-cream clouds reflected in the water.  Among foreground rocks, two small fishermen dressed in caps and blue coats are visible, one holding a rod and the other a net.
name: Painting
